verbose_text: miRNAs have also been used to predict treatment response in PCa, with increased expression of miR-141, miR-146b-3p, and miR-194 predictive of biochemical recurrence, which has been described as the PSA value of at least 0.4 ng/ml followed by another increase [XREF_BIBR] in patients post radical prostatectomy [XREF_BIBR].
